WEBVTT

00:08:59.786 --> 00:09:02.749
or how do we embrace
this technology for success?

00:09:03.349 --> 00:09:04.971
Now, why should you care?

00:09:06.320 --> 00:09:08.788
Well, let me describe some applications.

00:09:09.748 --> 00:09:11.416
Prosperity.

00:09:11.440 --> 00:09:13.448
The first era of the internet,

00:09:13.472 --> 00:09:14.813
the internet of information,

00:09:14.837 --> 00:09:18.300
brought us wealth
but not shared prosperity,

00:09:18.324 --> 00:09:20.778
because social inequality is growing.

00:09:20.802 --> 00:09:24.785
And this is at the heart
of all of the anger and extremism

00:09:24.809 --> 00:09:28.409
and protectionism and xenophobia and worse

00:09:28.433 --> 00:09:31.015
that we're seeing growing
in the world today,